quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  10,15,"Ne nibasomelwa tsinyaali tsiefu tsili habulafu, balia abalekombanga okhubukana ninafu baboolanga mbu; “Lera Ikuruani ilali ino, nohomba oyikalukhanie (hatiti).” Boola mbu; “Shenyala okhuyikalukhania khukhwenya khwanje tawe. Esie shenondanga halali kalia kefimbulilungwa. Toto esie eritsanga nengosela Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, eshinyasio shieyinyanga ikhongo.”"
  10,16,"Boola mbu; “Nyasaye yenyanga, shindakhabasomele Ikurani ino tawe, ne shiyakhabamanyiye tawe. Ne toto ndakhamenya ninanyu tsimbaka tsinyinji kano nikashili. Koo, shimwikhonyelanga obwongo tawe?”"
  10,17,"Kho niwina omubii muno oyo okhushila ulia uchishilanga Nyasaye obubeyi, nende ufukulanga tsinyaali tsiefu? Toto abakholi bamabii shibakhabura tawe."
  10,18,"Nabo balamaanga ebilali Nyasaye tawe, ebilanyala okhubakhola eshibii shiosishiosi tawe nohomba okhubakhoonya tawe. Ne baboolanga mbu; “Bano nibo abalikhusabila imbeli wa Nyasaye.” Boola mbu; “Koo, mubolelanga Nyasaye akakorerwe mwikulu nende khushialo? Obutswenufu nobubwe. Abula obuleemu, ne niwoluyali muno ehale nende ako akabamutsokasinjia ninako.""
  10,19,"Ne Abandu shibali halali omukanda mulala, mana nibakabukhana. Ne likhayanga okhuba likhuwa liaranjilila okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, bakhakhalachilwe hakari wabu eshina khukalia akabakabukhanangamwo."
  10,20,"Ne baboolanga mbu; “Shiyakheshilibwe eshimanyisio shirula khu Nyasaye wuwe Omulesi?” Boola mbu; “Obumanyi bwa amakhuwa kefisa buli khu Nyasaye. Kho mana linde. Toto siesi endi ninanyu halala mubalia balindanga?”"